---
title: Veggie Koftas and Harissa Mayo with Sesame Wedges and Cumin Roasted Carrots
description: Spring has sprung! A new season of veg is ready for our plates, which is why we've created these Veggie Koftas and Harissa Mayo. Making the most of tender carrots by pairing them with plenty of spice, this dish is sure to put a spring in your step.
